{"tid":2122336,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[急問]BNO 5+1 visa可否一家四口簽左visa後再前後腳過英國","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T08:25:58.000Z","uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d11714a14f3e009ca514bf864925d3c6718337","tid":2122336,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來我個計劃係太太帶兩個仔女過去英國先<br />\n自己留喺香港做一年野<br />\n再搞掂埋啲物業買賣同工人份合約先過去<br />\n但我睇到下邊呢段嘢話有機會將來5+1之後<br />\n會影響轉BR<br />\n是咪真的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係有影響<br />\n咁影響大唔大同有冇辦法補救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下長文：<br />\n<br />\n&lt;BNO - 太空人?&gt;<br />\n<br />\n再一次。英國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UKOnceAgain/photos/a.112057323901093/143680637405428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUKOnceAgain%2Fphotos%2Fa.112057323901093%2F143680637405428&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6JdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=325dfa90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UKOnceAgain/photos/a.112057323901093/143680637405428</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;BNO - 太空人?&gt;<br />\n<br />\nBNO 政策既細節終於出爐，條文我就唔啦度講啦，相信大家已經响唔同渠道睇到。<br />\n<br />\n不過相信其中一樣大家好關心既問題，就係可唔可以父母其中一人留响香港做嘢，而令一人帶小朋友過嚟英國(即係做太空人)。等我用我哋自身申請既經驗同大家解釋一下。<br />\n<br />\n條文中提到：<br />\nBN(O) citizens and their family dependants will be eligible to apply for Indefinite Leave to Remain in the UK after five years&rsquo; residence in the UK, subject to immigration rules.<br />\n<br />\n以我哋幫小朋友申請 Visa 為例，我哋一開始就係幫佢申請 Settlement Visa，然後就用呢個Visa 响英國換 BRP (British Residence Permit)，BRP 上面寫明佢有 Indefinite Leave to Remain，而呢張 BRP ￼ 係有限期，有需要既時候係要續領￼￼￼￼￼￼。換言之我哋幫小朋友申請既 Visa 就直接係 Indefinite Leave to Remain。<br />\n<br />\n關鍵就係，申請呢個 Visa 既時候係需要父母既名一齊落申請表，可能大家會諗，落名申請冇問題，不過當小朋友要轉做 citizen 既時候，係需要睇晒全家人响英國逗留既日數，要符合相關要求，如果唔係全家人都响英國逗留足夠既日數，佢係唔會俾小朋友轉英籍，更壞既情況就係續唔到個 BRP，或者會俾人問長問短。<br />\n<br />\n搬字過紙咁諗，如果唔係全家人响英國住夠規定日數，英國政府係 1）5年後唔會批 Indefinite to Remain 或 2）5+1年後唔會批入籍，甚至乎，如果達唔到5年內既居住日數，佢可以唔續 Visa 俾你，或者續期既時候會好麻煩(Agent 有提及過)。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家有所行動之前，最好做足一切準備，同埋諮詢下移民顧問或呢方面既專家，已策安全。不過其實做太空人真係唔容易，我哋試過三個月都覺得下不為例，大人細路都好辛苦！<br />\n<br />\n條文簡介：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fbritish-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6JdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=317db91a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n條文詳細：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fhong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6JdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=8a94cd29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement</a>"},{"pid":"f635242d04c0f49a69a808faf25c53ecee4346eb","tid":2122336,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"一日未出你一日都未知，不過我估得"},{"pid":"b0d0a1756119b35279c024d0090ec37d65542b5a","tid":2122336,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f635242d04c0f49a69a808faf25c53ecee4346eb","tid":2122336,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:02:11.